181
01:30:08,615 --> 01:30:13,078
[SPEAKER_19]: So this is also in addition to closing the budget gap we wanted

182
01:30:13,973 --> 01:30:34,879
[SPEAKER_19]: put back some spending that was previously cut so we're proposing to add back the art teacher at the high school and the inclusion specialist district wide and then additional funds to fully fund our professional development plan for next year and adding

183
01:30:36,458 --> 01:30:40,859
[SPEAKER_19]: even though we cut contracted maintenance, we're adding $50,000 back.

184
01:30:42,299 --> 01:30:44,980
[SPEAKER_19]: So we're pretty close to what was asked for in that account.

185
01:30:48,300 --> 01:31:05,203
[SPEAKER_19]: So this is just a recap of the elements of how we close the budget gap and we get that down to zero because we want to be able to make sure we're aligned with the funds the city provides for us.

