200
01:32:28,805 --> 01:32:33,928
[SPEAKER_19]: So, most of our employees belong to a union and the,

201
01:32:34,677 --> 01:32:39,119
[SPEAKER_19]: There's contracts negotiated over salaries and terms and conditions of work.

202
01:32:40,464 --> 01:32:52,433
