203
01:32:52,453 --> 01:32:56,276
[SPEAKER_19]: So their salary is set by school department policy.

204
01:32:57,097 --> 01:33:05,223
[SPEAKER_19]: And we budget money every year in order to give those people some raises.

205
01:33:06,764 --> 01:33:13,512
