403
01:48:55,491 --> 01:49:01,035
[SPEAKER_03]: So they're not served by air handling units, but they're served by unit ventilators.

404
01:49:01,195 --> 01:49:05,538
[SPEAKER_03]: So the air conditioning and ventilation is done through the unit ventilators.

405
01:49:06,819 --> 01:49:12,943
