406
01:49:16,805 --> 01:49:18,746
[SPEAKER_03]: and should be replaced.

407
01:49:19,526 --> 01:49:30,069
[SPEAKER_03]: The one part that I neglected to mention so far is that the air handling units have the cooling system is refrigerant based.

408
01:49:30,969 --> 01:49:31,669
[SPEAKER_03]: It's outdated.

409
01:49:32,429 --> 01:49:41,712
