[SPEAKER_03]: We can also come back to all these things later.

494
01:59:04,167 --> 01:59:09,511
[SPEAKER_21]: So we understand that Medford is interested in planning for the future, for future electrification.

495
01:59:09,851 --> 01:59:19,778
