501
02:00:17,215 --> 02:00:18,175
[SPEAKER_21]: or solar panels.

502
02:00:18,956 --> 02:00:37,073
[SPEAKER_21]: We will also be in the scope that we got priced, we're going to be putting down empty conduits from this new main electrical room up to the roof so that this PV project will be streamlined and it'll just be majority just a project up on the roof and we'll have everything already ready.

