857
02:35:20,026 --> 02:35:26,249
[SPEAKER_22]: And right now you have a very robust acoustically insulated area for equipment.

858
02:35:26,849 --> 02:35:29,470
[SPEAKER_22]: So option one, we don't have to study that.

859
02:35:29,610 --> 02:35:33,511
