02:35:33,531 --> 02:35:34,792
[SPEAKER_20]: Okay.

861
02:35:35,072 --> 02:35:37,933
[SPEAKER_20]: And then the third question, I don't really know if this makes a ton of sense.

862
02:35:39,153 --> 02:35:47,996
