[SPEAKER_02]: The pros and cons here.

900
02:39:14,890 --> 02:39:22,533
[SPEAKER_02]: What would probably be like the most like favored option in like other schools considering like the disturbances and like the cost efficiency?

901
02:39:22,553 --> 02:39:24,554
[SPEAKER_22]: Can I take that?

902
02:39:24,834 --> 02:39:26,815
[SPEAKER_22]: Yeah.

