02:40:24,942 --> 02:40:28,585
[SPEAKER_22]: We're maximizing the amount of solar on the roof with that option.

917
02:40:28,626 --> 02:40:35,112
[SPEAKER_22]: So I really feel personally that option one is the strongest because it has so many pluses.

918
02:40:39,243 --> 02:40:51,311
