02:40:51,371 --> 02:40:53,112
[SPEAKER_17]: So we're talking about the high school.

920
02:40:53,653 --> 02:40:55,714
[SPEAKER_17]: That might be a new building.

921
02:40:56,454 --> 02:40:59,957
