03:22:25,965 --> 03:22:28,968
[SPEAKER_07]: We just saw how the space summaries affect

1350
03:22:29,588 --> 03:22:51,456
[SPEAKER_07]: the plan and we want to just make sure there's a mechanism and a very clear mechanism so that every party knows what to expect and who is evaluating components and that the school committee can provide the feedback to the building committee on how things align with the mission since the building committee's mission is to create

1351
03:22:52,670 --> 03:22:57,177
[SPEAKER_07]: the mechanism for a high school that aligns with the educational plan.

1352
