1354
03:23:04,505 --> 03:23:25,549
[SPEAKER_06]: across all of the different groups, committees, groups, bodies that are involved in this project, whether it be the city of Medford, the school committee, the public school district, the comprehensive high school building committee, and all of them and how they work together.

1355
