[SPEAKER_07]: Yeah, exactly.

1356
03:23:26,869 --> 03:23:37,413
[SPEAKER_07]: And I think it's also a formal commitment to be collaborative in this process and not pitting education against physical space and whatever it is we were working together on this.

1357
