1385
03:24:46,594 --> 03:24:57,439
[SPEAKER_10]: Current language, educators use of Gen AI should be as a tool to support the teaching and learning environment, but is not to be solely relied upon in place of educator review and judgment.

1386
03:24:57,919 --> 03:25:00,140
[SPEAKER_10]: New language, educators use of Gen

1387
03:25:00,800 --> 03:25:09,622
[SPEAKER_10]: AI should be as a tool to support the teaching and learning environment, but is not to be solely relied upon in place of educator review and judgment.

1388
03:25:10,022 --> 03:25:14,743
[SPEAKER_10]: This is particularly true when assessing student essays and other qualitative work.

1389
03:25:15,283 --> 03:25:19,244
[SPEAKER_10]: Educators should not use AI tools to provide feedback or assign grades to students.

